      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation across three mesh densities yields GCI = 3.1% for NIH on the 5.8 M cell production mesh. Acceptance criterion satisfied. Assessment performed at nominal operating point; the same mesh topology is applied at all five COU points with the same spatial resolution, supporting extension of the GCI estimate."
