      "rationale": "Predicted NIH = 0.0031 mg/100 L vs. measured 0.0034 mg/100 L; relative error 8.8%. Criterion satisfied. Comparison performed exclusively at the nominal point (5 L/min, 3000 RPM); no output comparison is available for the four additional COU operating points where the linear superposition assumption underlying the damage model may be violated."
