      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; single experimental dataset is sufficient for validation comparison.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require statistical characterisation of experimental sample variability. Single hemolysis measurement set from a controlled in vitro circuit used. Sample assessment scoped out per MRL 2 guidance."
    },
